title: FxFactory 4.1.6 [Plugin After Effects Mac]
description:
Name: FxFactory
Version: 4.1.6

FxFactory powers hundreds of visual effects for Final Cut Pro, Motion, Premiere Pro and After Effects.

It's Faster
FxFactory uses the graphics card in your system to provide hardware-accelerated previews and rendering.

Requirements
OS X: Lion / Mountain Lion / Mavericks
Version 10.7, 10.8 and 10.9

Final Cut Pro: Versions 7 and 10
Motion: Versions 4 and 5
Adobe After Effects: CS5, CS5.5, CS6 and CC (Versions 10, 10.5, 11 and 12)
Adobe Premiere Pro: CS6 and CC (Versions 6 and 7)
